Perfect! I've fixed the STR upload CORS issue and pushed the changes to Railway. The fix addresses:

Fixed Endpoints
✅ /api/str/upload - STR bookings file upload
✅ /api/str/import-payout - Booking.com payout CSV import
Both endpoints now handle OPTIONS preflight requests without requiring authentication, just like the invoice upload fix.

What Was Fixed
The same issue as before - CORS preflight OPTIONS requests were being blocked by the @cognito_required decorator. I restructured both endpoints to:

Handle OPTIONS requests without authentication
Apply authentication only to POST requests
Deployment
The fix has been pushed to GitHub and Railway will automatically redeploy in 2-3 minutes.

